body:
Accept the tips and hush.  If you're playing and building entirely wrong and FEEDING, your way of play isn't the correct way. Stop thinking cause' someone suggests you prioritize your build or use a spell a different way, they are flaming you. It's your fault your KDA is where it sits, not your team or your enemy, you. It's no different than a tutor giving you lessons in math, they aren't flaming you to be better, they are instructing you of what works. Stop getting so butt hurt and being stubborn and sit down. 
and just to be cringy, "you need to calm down, cause' you're being to loud." 
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
